title: D.I.C.E. Announces Game of The Year Nominees! - Kinda Funny Games Daily 03.24.21
description:
Blessing and Janet talk about DICE Awards, It Takes Two reviews, and a new studio from Ikumi Nakamura.  

Follow Janet: https://twitter.com/Gameonysus

Time Stamps - 
00:00:00 - Start
00:03:45 - Housekeeping
Our It Takes Two Review is up right now as a Kinda Funny Gamescast. Me, Greg, and Tim have played the game. If you want a breakdown of our full thoughts you can catch that over on the Gamescast podcast feed or on YouTube.com/KindaFunnyGames
Thank you to our Patreon Producers:
Mick @DaNanoBiologist Abrahamson, Black Jack, & Trent Berrie
The Roper Report   -
00:05:00 - The 24th Annual Dice Awards were just announced - their website
00:31:00 - It Takes Two review round up
00:33:22 -  Ex-Ghostwire: Tokyo Director, Ikumi Nakamura, opens a studio - Jordan Oloman\
00:40:30 -  Ad
00:43:15 - Nintendo Confirms Download Codes for Super Mario 3D All-Stars Will Work After March 31 - Adam Bankhurst @ IGN
00:48:05 - We’ve got details on Hitman 3’s next DLC - Matt Purslow @ IGN
00:51:00 - Out today
 Reader mail   -
00:52:33 - Should Microsoft possibly buying Discord worry Sony at all? - Jordan Rowan
00:57:11 - Squad Up:Snoochie Coochie(PC) - ShoniesChonies
00:59:00 - You‘re Wrong
Tomorrow’s Hosts:Tim and Tam
